data.description: Welcome to your new home!  Somerset Chase is centrally located on the East side of Orlando.  Close to shopping, toll roads, and Valencia College.  This 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath townhome has open concept living area and 42 inch Cabinets in the kitchen area that boasts of stainless steel appliances and granite countertop and backsplash tile. Relax and unwind on the exterior patio area that overlooks the calming lake behind the home. Find complete serenity in one of the three spacious bedrooms that are located on the upper level of the home.  This home is also equipped with a two car garage for your convenience.  Schedule your showing today.
